Happy birthday Grandpa Marvin
We Love and miss you so much! ❤️ wish I could get one of your big bear hugs! And you could have meet your new great Grandson wai’olu 🤗
Mama and all her Grandkids! Thanks @hanamauicreate for everything you do for our family!  Wai’olu’s loved his first Christmas with all his Cusin’s 🎄❤️
Wai’olu’s first surf!  And looks like he’s regular foot like mom and Dad 🤣 barrel stance on point! hahah can’t wait to surf around the world with my loves @monycaeleogram and our little man! ❤️
Happy birthday brada @beneleogram we love and miss you! wai’olu is a lucky boy to have you as an Uncle! can’t wait to see you and @lenamaui  very soon! 🎉🥳

First dunk🐠🫶🏼💙 
Such good timing having @shannonsaylesphoto at the beach last weekend to catch this fun first for us and Wai’olu. Our little water babe💚

My beautiful valentines ❤️ @monycaeleogram baby Wai’olu 
And the best Bolognese meatball pasta 👌🏽 what more could I ask for 🤩
Wai’olu loves his @surfersjournal especially @danekealoha barrel’s!thanks uncel @chrissanita for the subscription!
Happy Mother’s Day to these special mamas! @monycaeleogram and @hanamauicreate  love and appreciate you both so so much ❤️
Happy Mothers Day to the coolest mama I know! Wai’olu is one lucky little guy to have you for a mom! We love you so so much @monycaeleogram thanks for everything you do❤️

Happily married for 10 years with my best friend @monycaeleogram ❤️ 🍾 enjoyed every second of it! I look forward to the fun and new memories we will create together  with our little guy by our side 💙
Happy anniversary monyca ❤️ love you more then words can describe 😘

Happy Surf Day 🌊💙

Had to get the picture with da champ @john_john_florence in the background showing us how to barrel ride like the barrel master he is! Hopefully one day wai’olu can barrel ride like you 🤙🏽

Happy 1st birthday wai’olu! Your a radical little guy and I love every second hanging with you! 💙
It’s been an amazing year following you around living and loving every second with you and @monycaeleogram

Happy birthday beautiful mama @monycaeleogram ❤️ 
Wai’olu and i are so lucky to be so loved by you, you amazingly beautiful, bad ass mamma! We love you so much! Have a wonderful year full of love laughter and adventure 😘

Fun day on bikes with the fam and friends! @murfelectricbike

Mexico 🇲🇽 fun!

It’s not all surfing and skating! Gotta make the boy work sometimes 😝💚 #mylittlefarmer 
Picking tangelos for @manafoods  and making fruit basket for our cottage  @monycaeleogram

L I V I N G ❤️
So grateful to share the stoke of snowboarding with my boy wai’olu and beautiful wife @monycaeleogram what an epic start to the New Year 🎆 sound up 🔉

First day back from snowboarding I find wai’olu on the skateboard by himself, I ask him do you want to go skateboarding? And he nods and says yup and grabs his helmet 😂 we head to the park and he runs some laps to warm up and jumps on his board and throws me a double Shaka 🤙🏽
